{"tid":1910403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生:警告中立/暗黃店,再唔表態就向外宣傳你係藍","createTime":"2020-03-04T15:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T16:46:29.000Z","uid":283912,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"838e9ebfed34de4caf607f812d6859489cccb470","tid":1910403,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8dyHr2lneOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8dyHr2lneOY&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=ff2fd098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8dyHr2lneOY</a><br />\n<br />\n7:15開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白票黨棄選撚最近全面進場擾亂視線<br />\n不斷同你講功能組別冇得贏,贏到都冇用<br />\n美國當你認可制度,國際會以為香港有民主..<br />\n點解仲有大半年先選五毛咁早開定工?<br />\n因來原來功能組別選民登記得返個幾月<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>5月2日就截止,轉界別嘅4月2日就截</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好覺得功能組別唔關自己事<br />\n實情你我都有野可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n~搵幫襯開/認識嘅暗黃/中立店<br />\n[black]~[/black]要佢地表態同幫佢地趕deadline登記選民<br />\n<br />\n~齊齊inbox炸所有黃店提佢地<br />\n[black]~[/black]據我所知仲有好多黃店十下十下未登記<br />\n<br />\n~呼籲各黃藍地圖app偉大admin們幫手宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行動po你唔係唔推阿<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e182780cf07c411d357a86eba8c093fc547437","tid":1910403,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NATghsp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNATghsp.gif&h=37891703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 分化同路人 趕走淺黃 拉 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0B1T4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\